{"id": 1495, "genre": 1001, "title": "这年头你还会出于哪些理由关注一个明星？", "description": "本以为自己早就过了追星的年纪，怎么又开始悄悄刷起了某些人的动态……（题图来自：Ana Galvañ）", "record_count": 3145, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170210164009bqkRlJI7smZPv3e0.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-15T03:00:57Z", "options": [{"id": 167169, "content": "脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937240}, {"id": 167425, "content": "某一瞬间的触动吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938296}, {"id": 167681, "content": "胡歌。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908031}, {"id": 178434, "content": "颜值演技内涵修养", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 968024}, {"id": 167427, "content": "真实", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938265}, {"id": 168195, "content": "艳照", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940074}, {"id": 167172, "content": "搞笑的，敢爱敢恨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935985}, {"id": 172292, "content": "演技，人品，性格", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 947004}, {"id": 174084, "content": "才华和三观，当然，脸也不能差", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956253}, {"id": 167173, "content": "表情包", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834708}, {"id": 167685, "content": "我个00后追张惠妹七年了，开始是因为作品，后来爱上了歌声，然后敬佩人品……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242921}, {"id": 176133, "content": "有自己的信仰与坚持", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951803}, {"id": 177414, "content": "一时间对上感觉的~然后慢慢了解~就会越来越喜欢~", "image": "img/option/option/20170310183154ARSzVq9wW83UY4pt", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953473}, {"id": 167431, "content": "他/她演绎的某个或某些角色与自己的某些特质有相似之处。同感吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938308}, {"id": 168455, "content": "当自己真的可以闲下来的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940824}, {"id": 166921, "content": "声音", "image": "img/option/option/20170215144012vUToKGH68MzZgDcY", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928618}, {"id": 167433, "content": "因为作品而关注他，再由人品而喜欢他，后于颜值而无法自拔。", "image": "img/option/option/20170216145519Bz2yDalon4QKPOYS.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5816}, {"id": 167689, "content": "胡歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 917730}, {"id": 169737, "content": "因为剧中人设，然后想看看真实的人是怎么样的。关注了一下觉得很无趣就又取关了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 561493}, {"id": 167178, "content": "一切让人喜悦、悲伤、互动的交集油然而生时", "image": "img/option/option/20170215221027Xj1iUpCcFBMyRYLr.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925912}, {"id": 170250, "content": "因为帅 因为搞笑?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945562}, {"id": 166923, "content": "剧中人设", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 932139}, {"id": 167179, "content": "张敬轩", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1125523}, {"id": 166924, "content": "演技好，角色吸引人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937268}, {"id": 167180, "content": "我還是比較喜歡有書香氣息的明星……", "image": "img/option/option/20170215221757oXIak2Dmi7znPBJE.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937731}, {"id": 171020, "content": "没事儿闲的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943391}, {"id": 166925, "content": "因为笑和抽", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937279}, {"id": 167181, "content": "始于颜值，陷于才华，终于人品", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252202}, {"id": 167437, "content": "不断涌现的新女团！！！", "image": "img/option/option/20170216150140Jh3pxSWXyfNlsPM9", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 357358}, {"id": 167949, "content": "马天宇  给正能量", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 939462}, {"id": 168973, "content": "歌唱深情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895637}, {"id": 169741, "content": "逼哥李志", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 762288}, {"id": 171533, "content": "出不出轨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949224}, {"id": 166926, "content": "花边新闻", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 558600}, {"id": 167182, "content": "斯蒂芬-库里", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921350}, {"id": 168206, "content": "我竟然，我竟然没见过ta这样的人设，还有好多黑历史像宝藏一样可以挖掘太有意思了233333", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940094}, {"id": 166927, "content": "喜欢这人饰演的角色，然后开始关注点点滴滴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113262}, {"id": 167183, "content": "有足够吸引我的地方。\n比如说薛之谦", "image": "img/option/option/20170215223232HbJjcXqRhOoCaYrB", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 695128}, {"id": 167439, "content": "因为张艺兴的三观很正，和我的想法很符合，性格很好", "image": "img/option/option/20170216151352qSvNbCkftlmaZu4T", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938337}, {"id": 167695, "content": "爱情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938927}, {"id": 171023, "content": "CHRISLEE！一见钟情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 947423}, {"id": 166928, "content": "爱哭也算一点。永远年轻 永远热泪盈眶。林漫威", "image": "img/option/option/20170215145732C2TPAY6aHuXstxgR.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937282}, {"id": 167440, "content": "靠感觉……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938340}, {"id": 167952, "content": "不作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 939468}, {"id": 168464, "content": "开始的一点点好感，也许就是他的一句话，一个动作，一个表情，然后慢慢的了解，特意去搜索“哇，原来是他啊...”便悄悄地开始关注，可能一开始并不认为自己在“追星” 只是想要多了解他一些罢了，然后慢慢的演变成每天刷他的动态时，便大方承认被他圈粉 ----被刘维圈粉的小感慨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940855}, {"id": 168976, "content": "实力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 941641}, {"id": 171280, "content": "主要是她喜欢～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948309}, {"id": 166929, "content": "因为她可爱，充满元气，让人看了觉得开心?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651437}, {"id": 167185, "content": "颜值，先看颜值再看人品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277290}, {"id": 166930, "content": "说新垣结衣的，说清楚你们究竟喜欢她什么嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635555}]}